:[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test isolation"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — override "},{"code":"analytics","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" on "},{"code":"SearchContainer","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" directly, without"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"touching "},{"code":"CoreAnalyticsContainer","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Clean dependency graph"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — each module’s DI surface is fully within its own container"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swappability"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — if "},{"code":"CoreAnalytics","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is replaced, only the proxy property needs updating"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"anchor":"The-Composition-Root","level":2,"text":"The Composition Root","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The app target is the ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"composition root","type":"text"}]},{"text":" — the only place where all modules are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"imported and containers are wired together:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ App\/Sources\/AppDelegate.swift","","import FeatureAuth","import FeatureSearch","import CoreAnalytics","","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","    func application(","        _ application: UIApplication,","        didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?","    ) -> Bool {","        \/\/ Wire containers","        AuthContainer.shared = AuthContainer()","        SearchContainer.shared = SearchContainer()","        CoreAnalyticsContainer.shared = CoreAnalyticsContainer()","        return true","    }","}"]},{"level":2,"text":"Import Dependency Graph","type":"heading","anchor":"Import-Dependency-Graph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The correct architecture follows this pattern:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["CoreProtocols (protocols only — no Forge import)","       ^","       |","  Feature modules (each has its own Container)","       ^","       |","  App target (imports all modules, wires containers)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Key rules:","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"orderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Protocol modules define abstractions only — no Forge dependency needed","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Feature modules import protocol modules and Forge"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"ViewModels and services never ","type":"text"},{"code":"import","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" a concrete service module directly","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The app target is the only place that imports both protocol and concrete modules","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"anchor":"Best-Practices","level":2,"text":"Best Practices","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Keep containers ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"module-scoped","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" — if a container grows beyond its module’s","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"concerns, the module has too many responsibilities"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Make dependency properties ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"public","type":"text"}]},{"text":" — they are the module’s DI surface","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"